headline: Want to Own a Piece of SpaceX? EchoStar Just Might Be the Best Way In.
summary: EchoStar  has completely remade its balance sheet and its investment case.  Now, it’s a primary way to invest in Elon Musk’s privately held space-technology company, SpaceX.  Monday, EchoStar announced a deal to sell the company’s AWS-4 and H-block spectrum licenses to SpaceX.

headline: PAL Names Soloviev Group CEO Michael Hershman Honoree of 50th Annual Gala
summary: The Police Athletic League (PAL), one of New York City's largest and longest-serving youth nonprofits, will honor Michael Hershman, CEO of the Soloviev Group and a proud PAL alumnus, at its 50th Annual Superstar Gala on Wednesday, October 15th at The Pierre.
